---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import MembershipTier from '../components/ui/MembershipTier.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/ui/SectionHeading.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<PageLayout 
  title="Join BCC — Conservative Membership in Bastrop County"
  description="Become a member of Bastrop County Conservatives PAC. Participate in our endorsement process and help elect conservative candidates in Bastrop County."
  heading="Become a Member"
  subheading="Join the Bastrop County Conservatives and help us identify, support, and elect candidates who share our values."
>
  <div class="mb-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <p class="text-xl text-bcc-gray-600 mb-6 font-medium">
      Membership in the Bastrop County Conservatives isn't just a donation—it's a seat at the table. Our members participate directly in our endorsement process and form the core of our conservative bulwark in Central Texas.
    </p>
    <p class="text-bcc-red font-bold text-lg">
      Sign up for annual membership today and get one month free!
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Accordion -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto not-prose">
    <SectionHeading title="Frequently Asked Questions" centered={true} class="mb-10" />
    
    <div class="space-y-4" id="faq-accordion">
      <div class="border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center bg-white hover:bg-bcc-gray-50 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-bcc-navy" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-bold text-bcc-navy text-lg">How are membership dues used?</span>
          <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-bcc-navy transition-transform duration-300 pointer-events-none icon-chevron" />
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 py-4 border-t border-bcc-gray-100 text-bcc-gray-700 bg-white">
          <p>100% of your membership dues directly fund our efforts within Bastrop County. This includes candidate vetting, voter guides, marketing campaigns, and organizational events. Operating as a PAC allows us to put your money directly to work securing conservative victories.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center bg-white hover:bg-bcc-gray-50 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-bcc-navy" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-bold text-bcc-navy text-lg">Can I upgrade my tier later?</span>
          <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-bcc-navy transition-transform duration-300 pointer-events-none icon-chevron" />
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 py-4 border-t border-bcc-gray-100 text-bcc-gray-700 bg-white">
          <p>Yes. You can upgrade your membership tier at any time. Simply log into the member portal or contact us, and the prorated remainder of your current membership will be applied toward the upgraded tier.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center bg-white hover:bg-bcc-gray-50 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-bcc-navy" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-bold text-bcc-navy text-lg">Is my membership tax-deductible?</span>
          <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-bcc-navy transition-transform duration-300 pointer-events-none icon-chevron" />
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 py-4 border-t border-bcc-gray-100 text-bcc-gray-700 bg-white">
          <p>Contributions or gifts to the Bastrop County Conservatives PAC are not deductible as charitable contributions for federal income tax purposes. We operate as a registered Political Action Committee in the state of Texas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-lg bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex justify-between items-center bg-white hover:bg-bcc-gray-50 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-inset focus:ring-bcc-navy" aria-expanded="false">
          <span class="font-bold text-bcc-navy text-lg">Who can join the BCC?</span>
          <Icon name="lucide:chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-bcc-navy transition-transform duration-300 pointer-events-none icon-chevron" />
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 py-4 border-t border-bcc-gray-100 text-bcc-gray-700 bg-white">
          <p>Any liberty-minded individual who aligns with our 15 Core Values is welcome to join. You must be a United States citizen or lawfully admitted permanent resident, and be at least 18 years old to contribute to the PAC. BCC reserves the right to decline membership to any individual.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Donorbox Checkout -->
  <div id="checkout" class="mt-24 mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
    <SectionHeading title="Join & Checkout" centered={true} class="mb-10" />
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto not-prose">
      <p class="text-center text-bcc-gray-600 mb-8">
        Select your membership tier below to complete your registration. All contributions go directly to supporting conservative candidates and civic engagement in Bastrop County.
      </p>
      <div class="mb-10 bg-bcc-cream border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-bcc-navy mb-4">Membership benefits</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-bcc-gray-700">
          <li><strong>Bronze</strong> membership includes an invite for participation in the candidate endorsement process and periodic updates on topics of interest.</li>
          <li><strong>Silver</strong> membership includes all Bronze benefits plus a BCC T-shirt.</li>
          <li><strong>Gold</strong> membership includes all Silver benefits plus a BCC polo or Pinpoint Oxford shirt.</li>
          <li><strong>Platinum</strong> membership includes all Gold benefits plus free access to our paid events.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-bcc-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <Fragment set:html={`
          <script src="https://donorbox.org/widget.js" paypalExpress="false"></script>
          <iframe 
            src="https://donorbox.org/embed/become-a-member-85?a=b" 
            name="donorbox" 
            allowpaymentrequest="allowpaymentrequest"
            seamless="seamless" 
            frameborder="0" 
            scrolling="no" 
            height="900px" 
            width="100%" 
            style="max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height: none!important; margin: 0 auto; display: block;"
            allow="payment"
          ></iframe>
        `} />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</PageLayout>

<script>
  // Setup lightweight vanilla JS accordion
  const toggles = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle');
  
  toggles.forEach(toggle => {
    toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const isExpanded = toggle.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
      const content = toggle.nextElementSibling;
      const icon = toggle.querySelector('.icon-chevron');
      
      // Close all other accordions
      toggles.forEach(t => {
        if(t !== toggle) {
          t.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
          t.nextElementSibling?.classList.add('hidden');
          t.querySelector('.icon-chevron')?.classList.remove('rotate-180');
        }
      });
      
      // Toggle current
      if(isExpanded) {
        toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
        content?.classList.add('hidden');
        icon?.classList.remove('rotate-180');
      } else {
        toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
        content?.classList.remove('hidden');
        icon?.classList.add('rotate-180');
      }
    });
  });
</script>
